{"tid":626533,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人有青光眼/眼壓高問題","createTime":"2018-04-12T07:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T02:14:47.000Z","uid":150204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"31964a6705e51715a04bd7264b55a2d897bfb1d1","tid":626533,"uid":150204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:52:49.000Z","msg":"尋日對眼中間(鼻根)個位置好繃緊, 按落去有陣麻痺既感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n出現呢個徵狀既前一晚隻右眼眼白無啦啦有蜘蛛網狀既紅筋<br />\n滴左除紅筋眼藥水而家冇咁紅, 但鼻根位置仲係有少少繃緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfeel到應該係眼壓過高, 眼珠仲好似有D硬..<br />\n<br />\n好驚係青光眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申冇近視唔洗帶眼鏡更加唔洗帶CON<br />\n工作原因要日日長時間對住部電腦<br />\n番到屋企冇玩電腦但成日用手機睇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人有眼壓高既經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣算唔算係青光眼初期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n約左聽日下午睇眼科, 好撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6ca89c90d9c7d9cee14254e818896c594058e8","tid":626533,"uid":136302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T07:04:45.000Z","msg":"有青光頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a56f058b6ee179e0608a9c866fa5b1f73c0cf2e","tid":626533,"uid":181326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T00:59:51.000Z","msg":"青光眼症狀常伴隨勁頭痛！急性青光眼嚴重會盲！<br />\n利申，眼做過手術，手術後遺症，現在要常覆診"},{"pid":"f7dbbb0698f640766e8b514191e5bb4c9291d9ca","tid":626533,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T01:03:46.000Z","msg":"你咪去眼鏡鋪驗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一兩舊搞得搞<br />\n真係過高你先去診所專料<br />\n有時你這訓得唔好都會咁"},{"pid":"09e8dd255793fb4e599e359782ee959016d734e7","tid":626533,"uid":181326,"like":0,